  * tests/ubuntu_drivers.py: Allow test_system_driver_packages_performance()
    90s on ARM, as 30s is not enough on slow buildds.

 -- Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>  Tue, 12 Apr 2016 11:03:37 +0200

